Problem Statement
Gig workers—such as delivery partners and ride-share drivers—often face unpredictable earnings, opaque algorithmic decisions, and unexplained pay variations. There is no transparent mechanism for workers to verify whether platforms like Zomato, Swiggy, or Uber have paid them fairly for a particular task
GitHub Repository URL
https://github.com/Rishi-Lab17/Overnight_Hackathon_Abhishek_shetty/new/main
Key Features of Your Solution:
1. Earnings Verification Engine
2. Real-Time Pay Transparency Dashboard
3. Legal Resource Center
4. Auto-Generated Fairness Report
5. clean & Simple Streamlit Web Portal
Tech Stack You Are Using:
Frontend	Streamlit, HTML, CSS
Backend Logic	Python
Analytics	NumPy, Pandas
Visualization	Streamlit native charts / Plotly
Storage (optional)	SQLite / Firebase / Google Sheets
Deployment	Streamlit Cloud / GitHub Pages + API
Target for the Next Checkpoint
presentation and completion of code
